            <div class="_1v7xp38b" id="077VRrN6z0oYW8Y4nTEWw" role="button">
             <div class="_1v7xp38c _1v7xp388">
              <div class="nbbs0ea">
               Travel and hospitality
              </div><a data-track-element="masonry-brick-2" href="/solutions/travel-hospitality"><h3 class="nbbs0e8" weight="500">Deliver faster service from the start with our travel planning experiences</h3></a>
              <div class="_1v7xp389">
               <div class="_1j2kes8z5 nbbs0e1">
                <p>Great hospitality starts at your very first interaction. Fastly caches what others can’t, like dynamic content and API responses. We handle interactions at the edge, closer to your visitors, for faster experiences that feel better and reduce bounce.</p>
               </div>
              </div>
              <div class="_1v7xp38e">
