       <div class="_sticky_1ppx5_26 dwg-box dwg-display--grid dwg-position--sticky">
        <div class="_fade-text_1ppx5_92 dwg-box dwg-width--full">
         <span class="dwg-text dwg-font-family--sharp-grotesk-20-book dwg-font-weight--medium dwg-line-height--150% dwg-text-align--left dwg-box dwg-p--0 dwg-m--0 dwg-bg-color--transparent">With Dropbox you can <span class="_feature_1ppx5_48 _yellow_1ppx5_62 dwg-box" tabindex="0">edit and sign<span class="_inline-icon_1ppx5_80 dwg-lazy-icon--standard dwg-box dwg-display--inline-block"></span></span> your documents, <span class="_feature_1ppx5_48 _green_1ppx5_56 dwg-box" tabindex="0">collaborate<span class="_inline-icon_1ppx5_80 dwg-lazy-icon--standard dwg-box dwg-display--inline-block"></span></span> on projects, <span class="_feature_1ppx5_48 _purple_1ppx5_68 dwg-box" tabindex="0">search<span class="_inline-icon_1ppx5_80 dwg-lazy-icon--standard dwg-box dwg-display--inline-block"></span></span> across all your apps, and it happens in the same place you <span class="_feature_1ppx5_48 _magenta_1ppx5_74 dwg-box" tabindex="0">securely store<span class="_inline-icon_1ppx5_80 dwg-lazy-icon--standard dwg-box dwg-display--inline-block"></span></span> all your content. It’s that simple :)</span>
        </div>
       </div>
